paragraphs.title: Network graph
paragraphs.text:
val topo2 = sqlContext.sql("select distinct addr from ioeventlog").map(_.getString(0)).collect().map{s=>
    val s2 = s.split("#")
    val node1 = s2(0)
    val node2 = s2(1)
    (node1,node2)
}.toList.toDF("node1","node2")
/*edge csv*/
val nodeLink = topo2.map(s=>Array(s.getString(0),s.getString(1),"undirected")).collect.toList
/*node csv*/
val former = topo2.select("node1").distinct.map(s=>s.getString(0)).collect.map(s=>Array(s,0.toString)).toList
val later = topo2.select("node2").distinct.map(s=>s.getString(0)).collect.map(s=>Array(s,1.toString)).toList
val sshh= former ++ later

/*writer csv*/
import java.io.StringWriter
import au.com.bytecode.opencsv.CSVWriter
import scala.collection.JavaConversions._
import java.io.FileWriter
import java.io.BufferedWriter
 
val out = new BufferedWriter(new FileWriter("/Users/lynnjiang/Documents/node.csv"))
val writer = new CSVWriter(out)
writer.writeAll(sshh)
out.close()
